---
// Experience.astro
---

<section class="experience">

    <!-- ── 01 WHAT I LEARNED ── -->
    <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-number">01</div>
            <div class="section-title-wrap">
                <h2>What I <span class="underline-word">learned</span> this year 😊</h2>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-value">1</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Transformative school year</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-value">∞</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Lessons & reflections</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-value">100%</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Commitment to students</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cards-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon" style="background:#fef3cd;">🔍</div>
                <h3>Hands-On Practice</h3>
                <p>From classroom observations to microteaching with peers, every task moved beyond theory into real, applied situations that shaped my teaching identity.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon" style="background:#e8f4fd;">🔄</div>
                <h3>The Cycle of Reflection</h3>
                <p>Teaching is a continual loop of learning, applying, and evaluating. Every lesson plan and feedback session taught me something new about the educator I want to become.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon" style="background:#fde8e8;">🤝</div>
                <h3>Power of Collaboration</h3>
                <p>Support from groupmates and instructors helped me refine my skills and discover perspectives I hadn't considered — a reminder that no teacher grows alone.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon" style="background:#e8f8f5;">⚖️</div>
                <h3>Balance & Resilience</h3>
                <p>Balancing coursework, field study, and personal life was challenging — but it sharpened my time management, organization, and the courage to ask for help.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── 02 FULL REFLECTION ── -->
    <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-number">02</div>
            <div class="section-title-wrap">
                <h2>My full <span class="underline-word">reflection</span></h2>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reflection-layout">
            <div class="reflection-sidebar">
                <p class="side-label">Key quote</p>
                <blockquote>
                    "Teaching is a continual cycle of learning, applying, and evaluating."
                </blockquote>
                <p class="author">— Personal reflection, this year</p>
            </div>
            <div class="reflection-body">
                <p>Looking back at this course  this school year to be exact  I can honestly say it has been an eye-opening and transformative experience. From the very beginning, I came in with an open mind and a desire to learn, but I didn't expect to grow in so many different ways, both professionally and personally.</p>
                <p>The course gave me the chance to dive deeper into the practical side of teaching. It wasn't just about theory. It was about applying what we learned in real, hands-on situations, whether through classroom observations, microteaching with my peers, or working on projects like the ePortfolio.</p>
                <p>I learned that being an effective educator requires so much more than just knowing the content; it's about connecting with students, adapting to their needs, and being flexible enough to change course when things don't go as planned.</p>
                <p>One of the most valuable takeaways was the emphasis on reflection — that it leads to growth. While there were challenges with balancing coursework, field study, and personal responsibilities, those challenges ultimately made the experience even more meaningful.</p>
                <p>Overall, this course has not only provided me with the tools and knowledge I need to teach, but also reminded me of <strong>why I want to be a teacher in the first place</strong>: to make a difference in the lives of students.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── 03 HEARTFELT ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS ── -->
    <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-number">03</div>
            <div class="section-title-wrap">
                <h2>Heartfelt <span class="underline-word">acknowledgements</span> 🌸</h2>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ack-grid">
            <div class="ack-card">
                <p>Thank you for guiding me, sharing your knowledge, and encouraging me to grow. Your mentorship shaped the teacher I am becoming.</p>
                <div class="ack-person">
                    <div class="ack-avatar">👩‍🏫</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="ack-name">Mentors & Cooperating Teachers</div>
                        <div class="ack-role">Field Study Supervisors</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ack-card">
                <p>Thank you for letting me be part of your learning journey. Your smiles, curiosity, and energy made every single day in the classroom worthwhile.</p>
                <div class="ack-person">
                    <div class="ack-avatar">🧒</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="ack-name">My Students</div>
                        <div class="ack-role">The heart of this journey</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ack-card">
                <p>To my groupmates — thank you for the late nights, shared laughs, honest feedback, and the kind of teamwork that made every challenge lighter.</p>
                <div class="ack-person">
                    <div class="ack-avatar">👫</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="ack-name">Groupmates & Peers</div>
                        <div class="ack-role">Pre-Service Teachers</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ack-card">
                <p>To my family and friends — thank you for your endless love, patience, and encouragement. I could not have done any of this without you.</p>
                <div class="ack-person">
                    <div class="ack-avatar">❤️</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="ack-name">Family & Friends</div>
                        <div class="ack-role">My greatest support system</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</section>

<style>
    :root {
        --cream: #f5f0e8;
        --ink:   #1a1a18;
        --gold:  #e8b84b;
        --border: #d4cfc4;
    }

    .experience {
        background: var(--cream);
        color: var(--ink);
        font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 300;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .section-inner {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 80px 48px;
        border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
    }

    .section-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    .section-number {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: 4rem;
        line-height: 1;
        color: var(--border);
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .section-title-wrap h2 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .underline-word {
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-decoration-color: var(--gold);
        text-decoration-thickness: 3px;
        text-underline-offset: 4px;
    }

    /* Stats */
    .stats-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
        border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
        margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    .stat-item {
        padding: 32px 28px;
        border-right: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
    }

    .stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }

    .stat-value {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .stat-label {
        font-size: .8rem;
        letter-spacing: .1em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #888;
        margin-top: 6px;
    }

    /* Cards */
    .cards-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
    }

    .card {
        padding: 36px 32px;
        border-right: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
        border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
        transition: background .2s;
    }

    .card:nth-child(2n)       { border-right: none; }
    .card:nth-last-child(-n+2) { border-bottom: none; }
    .card:hover { background: #ede8de; }

    .card-icon {
        width: 44px;
        height: 44px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        border: 2px solid var(--ink);
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .card h3 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .card p {
        font-size: .92rem;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.75;
    }

    /* Reflection */
    .reflection-layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
        border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
    }

    .reflection-sidebar {
        border-right: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
        padding: 36px 28px;
        background: var(--ink);
        color: #f5f0e8;
    }

    .side-label {
        font-size: .7rem;
        letter-spacing: .14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        opacity: .6;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .reflection-sidebar blockquote {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
        padding-left: 16px;
    }

    .reflection-sidebar .author {
        font-size: .82rem;
        opacity: .7;
    }

    .reflection-body {
        padding: 44px;
    }

    .reflection-body p {
        font-size: .97rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: #3a3a36;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .reflection-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    /* Acknowledgements */
    .ack-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 24px;
    }

    .ack-card {
        border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
        padding: 32px 28px;
        background: #fff;
        position: relative;
        transition: transform .2s;
    }

    .ack-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }

    .ack-card::before {
        content: '"';
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: 5rem;
        color: var(--border);
        position: absolute;
        top: 8px;
        right: 20px;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .ack-card p {
        font-size: .92rem;
        color: #444;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .ack-person {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
    }

    .ack-avatar {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--border);
        border: 2px solid var(--ink);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .ack-name {
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: .88rem;
    }

    .ack-role {
        font-size: .78rem;
        color: #888;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .section-inner      { padding: 56px 20px; }
        .cards-grid,
        .ack-grid           { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .card:nth-child(2n) { border-right: 1.5px solid var(--ink); }
        .card:nth-last-child(-n+2) { border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ink); }
        .card:last-child    { border-bottom: none; }
        .stats-grid         { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .stat-item          { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ink); }
        .stat-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .reflection-layout  { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .reflection-sidebar { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ink); }
    }
</style>